                    "id": "PRRC_kwDOFcwZ1c5y19B4",
                    "body": "I think you should be able to remove some of the boilerplate by using [Filter.HasBasis.tendsto_iff](https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Order/Filter/Bases.html#Filter.HasBasis.tendsto_iff), applied to [IsLinearTopology.hasBasis_twoSidedIdeal](https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Topology/Algebra/LinearTopology.html#IsLinearTopology.hasBasis_twoSidedIdeal) and [Filter.atTop_basis](https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Order/Filter/AtTopBot.html#Filter.atTop_basis).",
